Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]CHANNEL_WALLOP [-|^]<count> [action]
  This is activated whenever notice was sent to channel operators.
  The parameters for this function are:
    $0    The channel name
    $1    User that sent the notice
    $2-   The notice itself
